section.div: Favorites genres: Action, Comedy, Drama, Fantasy, Romance

div.div:
How can you fall in love when you can’t even hold hands? Due to a childhood curse, anything that the Duke touches will die—which makes his flirty maid’s behavior all the more shocking! Is there a way for the Duke and his companions to somehow break the curse, or is he doomed to a life where love is forever out of his reach?
(Source: Funimation)
Comedy, Fantasy, Romance, Slice of Life

The second season of Hataraku Maou-sama! MgRonald’s best demon lord worker is back, climbing the corporate ladder to become ruler of Earth. But Maou’s plans of domination might need to be put on hold when a small girl claims to be his and Emi’s child! (Source: Crunchyroll)

When Princess Alisa is framed for a terrible crime, she is shocked to learn that her own family wants her executed. Feeling defeated, she finds herself reborn as the princess of a rival empire. And though her new family acts sweet and kind on the surface, she’s not sure they can be truly trusted. Luckily, with this new life comes new power. But what exactly is this mysterious magic that awakens in her? And more importantly, can she use it to get vengeance against those who once betrayed her?
(Source: Tapas)

The story follows a unambitious introverted middle school student called Saike Kuzushiro. After witnessing the death of his childhood friend, Mikan Karatachi, in a road accident. He cries out to God and after a fall, Saike wakes up in bed the previous morning, the day of the accident. Will history repeat? Can he save Mikan? What power does he have to change the future? Included one-shots: Volume 3: The Negatibrain

div.span: Turbulent Adventurers are Introverted, Observant, Feeling, Prospecting and Turbulent. Adventurers are flexible and charming, always ready to explore and experience something new. They tend to have open minds, approaching life, new experiences, and people with grounded warmth.
Mostly Introverted. Likely prefers fewer, yet deep and meaningful, social interactions and feels drawn to calmer environments.
Mostly Observant. Likely pragmatic and down-to-earth, with a strong focus on what is happening or very likely to happen.
Mostly Feeling. Likely values emotional expression and sensitivity, prioritizing empathy, social harmony, and cooperation.
Mostly Prospecting. Likely very good at improvising and adapting. Tends to be flexible and values novelty above stability.
Mostly Turbulent. Likely self-conscious, sensitive to stress, success-driven, perfectionistic, and eager to improve.
